</section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">So in this article, we have gone over different areas where ANNs are performing high, and relatively low to other algorithms. It is not just technical reasons, it also includes the business problem statements you are trying to solve. I hope it almost makes a clear picture in your mind, of why and when to use Neural Networks. So, let’s meet in another article over other questions we might generally have in the field of AI, till then I Tushar signing off!</p></div></div></div></section><?php include_once 'Elemental/footer.php'; ?>